	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're graduating — or celebrating someone who is — the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> This is a season of excitement tangled with fear: the pressure to choose a path, to succeed, to figure out who you are once the cap comes off. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "bible verses for graduates," "graduation card Bible verses," "verses for the class of 2026," or "what does the Bible say about the future" — the answer starts in one place: wherever you go from here, your Father goes with you, and your worth was never your GPA, your degree, or your résumé.`}
